---
title: Smash Double Beef Burgers with Burger Sauce and Sweet Potato Wedges
description: These smash burgers bring crispy, beefy goodness to your stovetop! Crunchy pickles and savoury caramelized onions are served atop an all-beef patty!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R1014_W30_CA_RB151289-9_Main_low-3e96e507.jpg
